WEBVTT

00:17.600 --> 00:19.600
-Guards!
-Here.

00:19.680 --> 00:22.240
-Punish Yan Zheng alone.
-Yes.

00:22.800 --> 00:23.720
-Carry it out!
-Marquis…

00:24.600 --> 00:26.080
Marquis, my husband truly knew nothing!

00:27.000 --> 00:28.120
He doesn't know a thing.

00:28.200 --> 00:28.920
-Marquis…
-Do it!

00:29.000 --> 00:30.640
-Stand back!
-Hold on.

00:52.040 --> 00:53.640
If you're going to punish him,
punish me too.

00:53.720 --> 00:55.680
I had a part in what happened today.

00:57.480 --> 00:58.680
What part could you have had?

00:58.760 --> 01:01.080
Miss Bengong,
this has nothing to do with you.

01:01.840 --> 01:04.760
I also knew that Mrs. Fan
took the prisoner.

01:05.440 --> 01:07.680
As a physician, knowing
and not reporting makes me guilty too.

01:07.760 --> 01:09.720
I'm just a physician.

01:11.560 --> 01:12.800
What does it matter
if I'm beaten to death?

01:14.440 --> 01:16.040
These are military regulations.

01:17.560 --> 01:18.400
Military regulations?

01:19.320 --> 01:20.280
Then I should kneel first.

01:27.480 --> 01:28.640
Wait!

01:34.680 --> 01:35.520
Marquis.

01:38.480 --> 01:40.160
Something happened at the cave.

01:40.800 --> 01:42.640
Shi Yue sent several top experts.

01:43.160 --> 01:45.200
They tunneled through the wall
trying to rescue Sui Yuanqing.

01:46.040 --> 01:48.680
If Mrs. Fan hadn't moved him just in time,

01:48.760 --> 01:50.680
that bastard might already be free.

01:52.200 --> 01:54.320
Yes, Mrs. Fan acted

01:54.400 --> 01:56.400
without authorization and violated orders,

01:57.040 --> 01:58.560
but she also protected the hostage.

01:59.840 --> 02:02.640
If you ask me,
that's merit offsetting fault.

02:03.240 --> 02:04.920
Don't you think, Mar…
Don't you think, Marquis?

02:08.960 --> 02:11.680
Since both the Strategist
and the Imperial Physician are pleading

02:12.320 --> 02:13.280
on her behalf,

02:14.000 --> 02:15.280
merit offsetting fault?

02:15.960 --> 02:16.840
Yan Zheng,

02:18.080 --> 02:19.960
what do you think?

02:35.360 --> 02:36.240
Thank you, Marquis.

02:37.680 --> 02:39.000
Thank you, Marquis.

04:06.160 --> 04:10.760
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

04:14.720 --> 04:16.839
Mrs. Fan is no ordinary woman.

04:16.920 --> 04:18.560
You should've seen it.

04:18.640 --> 04:20.279
Bags of salt, weight 50 or 60 jin,

04:20.360 --> 04:22.800
all four of them on her shoulders at once.

04:22.880 --> 04:24.000
Carrying salt bags,

04:24.080 --> 04:26.560
holding a roast whole lamb,
running faster than anyone.

04:26.640 --> 04:28.120
That heroic figure

04:28.200 --> 04:30.440
-is like a goddess descending to earth.
-Really?

04:30.520 --> 04:32.120
I also heard that

04:32.640 --> 04:35.560
when Mrs. Fan was moving bricks
at the Wu River camp,

04:35.640 --> 04:38.520
-she could carry 300 jin at a time.
-How much?

04:38.600 --> 04:39.920
-Three hundred jin.
-That much?

04:40.000 --> 04:41.040
-Who'd you hear that from?
-Incredible.

04:41.120 --> 04:43.520
-One basket was 300 jin.
-No way!

04:43.600 --> 04:45.120
She could carry two baskets by herself.

04:45.200 --> 04:46.160
Six hundred jin.

04:46.760 --> 04:48.200
-Six hundred jin?
-Oh my…

04:48.280 --> 04:49.280
Is there really someone that incredible?

04:49.880 --> 04:51.200
I recognize you now.

04:51.280 --> 04:53.600
You're the Pig Squad that earned merit

04:53.680 --> 04:55.080
following Mrs. Fan.

04:56.120 --> 04:58.040
Pig-Slaughter Squad.

04:58.120 --> 04:59.880
Right. The Pig-Slaughter Squad.

04:59.960 --> 05:01.440
-Come, brother, have a seat.
-Please take a seat.

05:01.520 --> 05:03.920
Come, have a seat.

05:06.520 --> 05:07.520
So that night,

05:08.360 --> 05:09.360
pitch black, wind howling,

05:09.440 --> 05:12.680
Mrs. Fan suddenly sensed
movement outside the camp.

05:12.760 --> 05:16.240
Then, bam, one kick, and she burst through

05:16.320 --> 05:18.600
that wooden door
bolted shut with iron chains.

05:18.680 --> 05:20.000
Mrs. Fan,

05:20.520 --> 05:22.720
with one kick, she smashed
through the camp gate.

05:23.320 --> 05:25.960
Alone on horseback, she chased ten miles
and killed the scouts.

05:26.040 --> 05:28.280
She kicked open
the camp's iron gate with one blow,

05:28.360 --> 05:30.040
-ran 80 miles without stopping,
-Eighty miles?

05:30.120 --> 05:32.760
and with one clean slice, came back
carrying the heads of three scouts.

05:32.840 --> 05:36.360
Mrs. Fan used to be a butcher.

05:36.440 --> 05:39.480
Everyone in Lin'an Town knew her.

05:39.560 --> 05:43.160
One slap
and she could knock out a big fat pig.

05:44.120 --> 05:47.640
Back then, she was magnificent,
heroic and bold.

05:47.720 --> 05:49.240
When fighting bandits,

05:49.320 --> 05:52.040
she took on a hundred all by herself
and never fell behind.

05:52.120 --> 05:54.040
She once kicked open a city gate.

05:54.120 --> 05:57.400
Thousands of bandit troops at the gate
couldn't hold against her alone.

05:57.480 --> 05:59.760
She charged into Shi Hu's camp alone,

05:59.840 --> 06:01.200
carrying four bags of salt,

06:01.280 --> 06:03.120
five bags of rice,
six baskets of vegetables,

06:03.200 --> 06:04.960
and four roast whole lambs,

06:05.040 --> 06:06.080
like she was walking through
an empty field.

06:06.160 --> 06:09.320
I also heard
she killed a bear with one slap.

06:10.680 --> 06:13.320
One good woman like that is worth ten men.

06:13.400 --> 06:14.600
She's really something.

06:14.680 --> 06:16.560
Her husband is one lucky guy.

06:16.640 --> 06:17.920
But

06:18.000 --> 06:19.840
her husband's pretty badly hurt this time.

06:19.920 --> 06:22.120
Keeps coughing up blood.

06:22.200 --> 06:24.200
Might not make it.

06:24.280 --> 06:25.320
He's dying.

06:25.400 --> 06:26.680
He's been moved to a private tent.

06:27.320 --> 06:29.720
Even if he survives,
he'll still be in bad shape.

06:29.800 --> 06:32.920
No wonder Mrs. Fan
only grabbed meat this time.

06:33.000 --> 06:35.400
She must be making
her husband his last meal.

06:36.280 --> 06:38.440
Now that's loyalty and love.

07:05.680 --> 07:06.920
Sister.

07:08.160 --> 07:09.680
Smelled the aroma
and followed it here, huh?

07:10.200 --> 07:11.920
Once the mutton soup is ready,
I'll save you a bowl.

07:15.560 --> 07:17.600
Where's your big brother
and that pig squad of his?

07:17.680 --> 07:21.200
While they're not around,

07:21.920 --> 07:23.680
there's something I want to tell you.

07:23.760 --> 07:24.680
Well…

07:25.600 --> 07:26.560
Go ahead.

07:27.680 --> 07:29.560
-I heard…
-Changyu.

07:29.640 --> 07:31.200
You're cooking.

07:31.280 --> 07:32.800
You arrived at just the right time.

07:32.880 --> 07:35.040
-When it's ready, I'll bring you a bowl.
-Good.

07:36.040 --> 07:37.840
-Go ahead.
-Smells wonderful.

07:43.240 --> 07:44.480
This kid…

07:45.080 --> 07:45.920
Changyu,

07:46.600 --> 07:49.480
I heard you once kicked open a city gate.

07:50.200 --> 07:52.200
Who could kick open a city gate?

07:52.800 --> 07:54.040
And I also heard

07:54.120 --> 07:58.120
you grabbed a lamb
to make your husband his last meal.

07:59.240 --> 08:00.200
They're just talking nonsense.

08:00.280 --> 08:01.120
Don't listen to them.

08:01.200 --> 08:02.680
Talking nonsense?

08:02.760 --> 08:05.480
If word of this
reaches the Marquis of Wu'an,

08:05.560 --> 08:08.360
he might just have their heads cut off.

08:10.120 --> 08:11.320
That seems a bit extreme.

08:11.880 --> 08:15.560
The Marquis of Wu'an,
apart from his slight stutter,

08:15.640 --> 08:18.120
seems like a decent sort to me.

08:18.800 --> 08:21.200
After all, he didn't
make things hard for us.

08:21.280 --> 08:24.120
I don't have anything good
to thank him with,

08:24.200 --> 08:25.520
but I made some

08:25.600 --> 08:27.880
mutton soup, some braised meat,
and a few stir-fried dishes.

08:27.960 --> 08:29.520
I'll have you take them to him.

08:31.240 --> 08:32.720
You don't blame
the Marquis of Wu'an anymore?

08:34.880 --> 08:36.640
How could I blame him?

08:36.720 --> 08:38.640
Every trade has its rules.

08:38.720 --> 08:39.919
Even us pig butchers

08:40.000 --> 08:41.840
have our way of doing things. We don't
throw in extras when selling pork,

08:42.440 --> 08:44.000
let alone when it comes to war.

08:44.680 --> 08:47.080
This time, I acted on my own.

08:47.160 --> 08:49.000
Luckily, reinforcements came to help.

08:49.080 --> 08:52.400
If they hadn't,
I might have died along with that bastard.

08:52.480 --> 08:53.960
What a waste that would've been.

08:54.560 --> 08:56.920
Next time, I'll follow orders.

08:57.000 --> 08:57.880
Fight wherever I'm assigned.

09:01.080 --> 09:03.320
To have a wife like you,

09:04.200 --> 09:06.200
he must have accumulated good fortune
over several lifetimes.

09:07.080 --> 09:08.120
Here, let me help you.

09:08.200 --> 09:10.320
Here, try a bowl.

09:10.400 --> 09:11.240
Okay.

09:11.320 --> 09:12.600
-Here.
-Here.

09:14.120 --> 09:15.600
-See if it needs more salt.
-Okay.

09:15.680 --> 09:17.600
XIE

09:19.760 --> 09:20.920
Yan Zheng.

09:25.480 --> 09:26.360
Eat up.

09:26.440 --> 09:27.480
Get your strength back.

09:28.560 --> 09:29.400
Aren't you eating?

09:30.120 --> 09:32.840
I couldn't resist while I was cooking.

09:32.920 --> 09:34.160
Already ate my fill.

09:58.760 --> 10:00.680
Your wounds aren't fully healed yet.

10:01.320 --> 10:02.360
You need to eat more…

10:03.680 --> 10:04.720
and recover properly.

10:25.920 --> 10:26.920
Today,

10:27.600 --> 10:29.360
when the Marquis of Wu'an punished us,

10:29.440 --> 10:30.600
aren't you angry?

10:32.040 --> 10:33.480
The Marquis was right to discipline us.

10:34.720 --> 10:38.480
The Pig-Slaughter Squad and I
got off easy this time

10:38.560 --> 10:39.680
only because we were lucky.

10:41.120 --> 10:44.240
Later, I'll ask Mr. Gongsun
about the military regulations.

10:44.320 --> 10:45.720
I promise it won't happen again.

10:46.320 --> 10:49.000
And if that Marquis of Wu'an
wants to punish you again,

10:49.080 --> 10:50.120
tell him to come to me.

10:50.200 --> 10:51.320
You're wounded.

10:51.400 --> 10:52.840
You can't take another punishment.

10:52.920 --> 10:54.000
I can take a beating.

10:58.200 --> 10:59.400
You've changed.

11:00.880 --> 11:03.600
Back in Lin'an,
you'd never admit you were wrong.

11:06.920 --> 11:08.720
After everything that's happened,

11:08.800 --> 11:10.240
how could I still be

11:10.320 --> 11:12.680
that little butcher girl who only knew
how to slaughter pigs and sell meat?

11:14.320 --> 11:17.600
As long as I get to beat the hell out
of that bastard Sui Yuanqing in the end,

11:18.520 --> 11:20.000
I'll follow whatever rules they want.

11:22.680 --> 11:24.560
Good. I promise you.

11:26.400 --> 11:27.560
What for?

11:27.640 --> 11:28.640
It's not like you're the one
calling the shots.

11:29.360 --> 11:30.600
Whatever you say,

11:31.560 --> 11:32.720
I'll agree to it.

11:39.760 --> 11:42.200
You need to drink this medicine
while it's hot too.

11:44.640 --> 11:45.800
Oh,

11:45.880 --> 11:48.760
when I was working on the dam,
I met an old gentleman.

11:49.360 --> 11:51.480
He's tough on the outside but soft inside.

11:52.000 --> 11:52.840
To save me,

11:53.440 --> 11:55.480
he even swapped
the life-and-death lots with me.

11:56.240 --> 11:57.200
If he did you a kindness,

11:57.280 --> 11:59.200
I'll give him a promotion or two
in the future.

12:01.000 --> 12:02.320
What could you possibly promote him to?

12:13.920 --> 12:15.200
I meant…

12:16.800 --> 12:17.680
in the future.

12:18.920 --> 12:23.080
You're that confident
you'll become a general someday?

12:35.720 --> 12:36.880
If…

12:38.040 --> 12:39.160
Just saying if…

12:41.880 --> 12:43.120
If someday

12:43.200 --> 12:45.520
I become an official
even bigger than a general?

12:46.280 --> 12:47.440
What kind of official?

12:49.600 --> 12:50.760
Like…

12:52.320 --> 12:53.760
being ennobled as a marquis.

12:56.760 --> 12:59.120
Ennobled as a marquis.

13:01.400 --> 13:03.200
Then this pig-slaughtering woman

13:03.280 --> 13:04.800
would be a marchioness, wouldn't I?

13:06.200 --> 13:07.120
Would you want that?

13:07.880 --> 13:09.240
Of course I would.

13:09.320 --> 13:11.480
Only a fool would say no
to something that good.

13:38.560 --> 13:40.040
Eat sparingly.

13:40.120 --> 13:41.480
I don't have many left.

13:59.840 --> 14:01.000
Come in.

14:02.840 --> 14:04.960
He's the strategist and your boss.

14:05.040 --> 14:06.800
Talking to him like that,
aren't you afraid he'll hold a grudge?

14:09.160 --> 14:10.480
There's so much going on in the army.

14:10.560 --> 14:12.680
Can't stand on ceremony all the time.

14:14.600 --> 14:15.840
Right?

14:16.360 --> 14:18.480
Right. Military affairs come first.

14:19.600 --> 14:21.520
You two talk. I'll go heat some water.

14:30.760 --> 14:31.880
Our plan worked.

14:32.400 --> 14:34.360
I heard you received
an urgent dispatch from Lucheng.

14:36.760 --> 14:39.880
Prince Changxin should be
gathering his main force.

14:41.280 --> 14:43.920
Probably planning a swift strike.

14:45.080 --> 14:46.480
Shi Yue and his rebel forces

14:46.560 --> 14:48.280
are shooting arrows
at Sui Yuanqing without restraint.

14:48.360 --> 14:50.320
That changes the nature
of the hostage situation.

14:51.120 --> 14:52.920
Before, they held back
fearing for the hostage.

14:53.000 --> 14:54.960
So a thousand of us are able
to hold off thirty grand of the enemy.

14:55.560 --> 14:56.840
But from what we saw today,

14:58.320 --> 15:01.160
that hostage isn't worth much anymore.

15:02.640 --> 15:03.800
Looks like…

15:05.320 --> 15:06.800
the decisive battle is imminent.

15:12.880 --> 15:13.720
Brother,

15:13.800 --> 15:15.480
the heir has made his position clear.

15:15.560 --> 15:17.040
He told us not to worry about him,

15:17.120 --> 15:18.360
just charge forward as planned.

15:20.120 --> 15:22.040
But that's the heir.

15:23.080 --> 15:25.280
How can we just stand by and watch?

15:25.360 --> 15:29.400
Today in battle,
he was accidentally wounded.

15:29.480 --> 15:31.800
You and I both know his nature.
He never forgets a grudge,

15:31.880 --> 15:33.040
goes off at the slightest thing.

15:33.120 --> 15:34.600
He won't let this…

15:35.520 --> 15:37.760
go quietly.

15:37.840 --> 15:39.880
You mean,

15:39.960 --> 15:40.880
after this,

15:41.600 --> 15:43.040
the heir won't go easy on us?

15:45.440 --> 15:47.920
Brother, the old prince's orders
are ironclad.

15:48.520 --> 15:49.880
If we fail this mission,

15:50.400 --> 15:52.720
our lives are forfeit anyway, Brother.

15:54.120 --> 15:56.360
If something happens to the heir,

15:57.480 --> 15:59.720
even if we secure the Prince's cause,

16:00.400 --> 16:02.360
once the heir takes the throne,

16:03.400 --> 16:05.720
our lives won't be worth living.

16:06.320 --> 16:08.280
We're stuck with this blame.

16:09.480 --> 16:11.240
Brother, no more hesitation.

16:11.320 --> 16:12.160
Make a call.

16:15.760 --> 16:16.720
Fine.

16:17.960 --> 16:19.200
Tomorrow, we attack with full force.

16:22.560 --> 16:24.520
Best case, we get the heir back.

16:24.600 --> 16:26.160
If not,

16:27.080 --> 16:29.040
we take Xie Zheng's head

16:29.840 --> 16:31.920
back to the Prince and answer for it.

16:34.840 --> 16:36.240
What's going on?

16:37.360 --> 16:39.560
Can't we talk here?

16:41.000 --> 16:41.920
What's with all the secrecy?

16:43.560 --> 16:44.600
Sister,

16:45.120 --> 16:47.240
I heard we're going into battle
in a few days.

16:48.000 --> 16:51.440
This is all the silver
I've saved since joining the army.

16:52.040 --> 16:55.240
And some that my brother gave me when
I was hanging around the gambling den.

16:56.000 --> 16:57.880
You hold onto it for me.

17:01.040 --> 17:03.000
Why not give it to your brother? Why me?

17:03.080 --> 17:05.200
My brother's going into battle too.

17:06.040 --> 17:07.079
You're not.

17:08.319 --> 17:10.359
You're the safest one to keep it.

17:11.720 --> 17:13.440
Bullets and blades have no eyes.

17:14.079 --> 17:16.200
If I die out there,

17:17.200 --> 17:19.440
please take this silver home

17:19.520 --> 17:21.160
to my little sister.

17:25.680 --> 17:26.839
-Okay.
-You're trying to make me angry?

17:27.440 --> 17:28.800
Who told you to say such unlucky things?

17:28.880 --> 17:29.960
What's all this about dying?

17:30.040 --> 17:31.000
Don't say another word.

17:32.200 --> 17:33.600
Do you know who your sister is?

17:34.680 --> 17:36.360
I got you all out safely.

17:37.000 --> 17:38.960
I'll get you all back safely.

17:39.520 --> 17:40.400
Every single one.

17:40.920 --> 17:42.080
You keep it yourself.

17:42.720 --> 17:44.280
If you leave it with me,

17:44.360 --> 17:47.120
when I go back to Lin'an,
I'll spend it all on pigs.

17:47.200 --> 17:48.520
Not a single coin left for you.

17:51.880 --> 17:54.480
Then… I'd be happy to buy pigs
for you, dear sister.

17:57.480 --> 17:59.080
Go to sleep now.

17:59.160 --> 18:00.800
No more of this nonsense.

18:03.400 --> 18:04.800
Got it, Sister.

18:31.440 --> 18:32.560
All troops, assemble!

18:35.520 --> 18:36.480
Move it.

18:41.120 --> 18:42.240
Hurry.

18:49.520 --> 18:50.840
Stay close together.

19:07.320 --> 19:08.480
Headmaster Gongsun,

19:08.560 --> 19:10.240
is everything in order…

19:11.440 --> 19:12.840
for this campaign?

19:14.440 --> 19:15.440
Rest assured,

19:15.520 --> 19:17.120
everything has been arranged properly.

19:17.200 --> 19:18.280
No need to worry.

19:23.080 --> 19:24.120
Your Highness.

19:25.960 --> 19:27.480
I must depart.

19:48.960 --> 19:50.360
Take this chess manual.

19:50.440 --> 19:51.680
Keep it safe.

19:54.280 --> 19:55.400
HIDDEN PRINCIPLES OF QI

19:55.480 --> 19:58.640
When I was young, I once saw
a fragment of a chess manual

19:58.720 --> 20:00.600
called Hidden Principles of Qi.

20:00.680 --> 20:01.520
This book,

20:02.120 --> 20:03.600
the Gongsun family library

20:03.680 --> 20:05.000
does have a complete edition.

20:05.600 --> 20:08.000
But it's my grandfather's
treasured possession.

20:08.520 --> 20:09.560
Not allowed to be lent out.

20:14.520 --> 20:15.960
On the battlefield,
swords and arrows have no eyes.

20:18.720 --> 20:20.960
Headmaster, you must be careful.

20:22.840 --> 20:25.440
With all these Xie soldiers protecting me,

20:25.520 --> 20:26.680
I'm sure I'll be fine.

20:27.280 --> 20:29.480
Besides, if I can't win, I'll just run.

20:38.600 --> 20:39.440
I await your…

20:40.920 --> 20:42.040
safe return, Headmaster.

21:11.960 --> 21:13.440
Brave sons of Dayin,

21:14.760 --> 21:15.720
all of you

21:16.480 --> 21:18.440
must also return safely.

21:22.240 --> 21:24.720
Marquis, the advance team
has deployed with the Strategist.

21:25.360 --> 21:26.480
Last night, the rebels

21:26.560 --> 21:28.200
secretly positioned
some of their troops in ambush.

21:29.280 --> 21:30.440
Depart immediately.

21:30.520 --> 21:32.400
Once the enemy is trapped,
press the advantage and pursue.

21:33.000 --> 21:33.840
Understood.

21:35.400 --> 21:36.360
Marquis.

21:37.840 --> 21:38.920
Mrs. Fan is here.

21:40.440 --> 21:41.720
You go ahead. I'll follow shortly.

21:41.800 --> 21:43.640
-Yes, sir.
-Yes, sir.

21:44.680 --> 21:47.080
General Wu, General Jiu.

21:47.160 --> 21:48.160
Madam.

21:57.280 --> 21:58.760
Your wound is still seeping blood.

21:59.320 --> 22:01.400
It's just a minor wound, nothing serious.

22:08.720 --> 22:09.600
Let me.

22:27.120 --> 22:27.960
Yan Zheng,

22:29.920 --> 22:32.560
how about I go to battle in your place?

22:33.600 --> 22:35.080
Don't be silly.

22:38.960 --> 22:40.400
Your wounds aren't healed yet.

22:41.160 --> 22:43.400
On the battlefield, you won't
even be able to lift your blade.

22:45.040 --> 22:46.360
What then?

22:50.600 --> 22:52.480
I'm just an infantry swordsman.

22:52.560 --> 22:55.080
My job is to clear the battlefield,
mop up the remnants.

22:56.040 --> 22:57.120
Nothing dangerous.

23:00.520 --> 23:02.040
Then be careful out there.

23:09.200 --> 23:10.120
Wait for me.

23:19.280 --> 23:20.320
The medicine's getting cold.

23:20.960 --> 23:21.840
Drink it while it's hot.

23:35.600 --> 23:36.640
Okay.

23:47.560 --> 23:48.480
Oh,

23:49.200 --> 23:51.840
and which infantry swordsman unit
are you in?

23:51.920 --> 23:53.560
Who's your commanding officer?

23:56.920 --> 23:58.560
Left Guard, Third Battalion.

24:01.920 --> 24:03.160
Why do you ask?

24:03.960 --> 24:04.880
Nothing.

24:05.600 --> 24:06.600
Just asking.

24:17.440 --> 24:18.840
If something happens…

24:21.320 --> 24:22.760
take care of Changning for me.

24:25.960 --> 24:27.000
You…

24:41.720 --> 24:42.760
Yan Zheng.

24:47.040 --> 24:48.800
I can't let anything happen to you.

25:02.240 --> 25:03.520
Emergency assembly!

25:03.600 --> 25:04.440
Quick!

25:04.520 --> 25:05.480
Emergency assembly!

25:05.560 --> 25:06.520
Move it!

25:27.920 --> 25:28.760
Wait for me.

25:36.000 --> 25:37.040
Here.

25:37.600 --> 25:38.440
Ning,

25:38.520 --> 25:39.800
remember what I told you.

26:20.560 --> 26:21.560
Boss.

26:21.640 --> 26:22.680
That's Sister.

26:28.840 --> 26:29.680
What are you doing here?

26:29.760 --> 26:30.840
Yeah, Sister. What are you doing here?

26:30.920 --> 26:32.000
What are you playing at?

26:32.080 --> 26:34.480
Sister, please go back, okay?

26:34.560 --> 26:35.600
The battlefield is brutal.

26:35.680 --> 26:36.840
You could die at any moment.

26:36.920 --> 26:38.600
Have you forgotten what happened
when the dam broke?

26:38.680 --> 26:39.640
I remember.

26:39.720 --> 26:41.640
That's why I can't let Yan Zheng
go to battle.

26:42.160 --> 26:43.240
I drugged him.

26:43.320 --> 26:45.680
If I don't take his place,
he really will become a deserter.

26:45.760 --> 26:46.640
You…

26:47.160 --> 26:48.600
Why are you so protective of him?

26:48.680 --> 26:50.360
Why don't you think
about yourself for once?

26:50.440 --> 26:51.600
This is war.

26:51.680 --> 26:52.840
Exactly.

26:52.920 --> 26:54.200
I know it's war.

26:55.200 --> 26:57.240
I'm just going to fill a spot.

26:57.320 --> 26:59.000
Once we get to the battlefield,

26:59.080 --> 27:01.880
we'll find a chance to cut off
a pair of ears from a dead body.

27:01.960 --> 27:03.640
That way, if the higher-ups find out,

27:03.720 --> 27:05.960
we can prove we fought.

27:06.040 --> 27:07.160
It's not that easy.

27:07.240 --> 27:08.400
It's not that easy!

27:08.920 --> 27:10.360
Let me ask you.
Who here has been to war before?

27:10.440 --> 27:11.280
Never been.

27:11.360 --> 27:12.880
-And the battlefield is so dangerous.
-What's all the noise?

27:14.440 --> 27:16.560
Which squad are you from?

27:16.640 --> 27:18.200
How'd you end up in my unit?

27:19.800 --> 27:23.080
We're from Left Guard, Third Battalion.

27:23.160 --> 27:24.640
Responsible for mopping up the remnants.

27:24.720 --> 27:25.840
-Third Battalion?
-Yes.

27:25.920 --> 27:27.040
Left Guard?

27:27.560 --> 27:28.960
There is no Third Battalion here.

27:29.040 --> 27:30.400
There's only our Vanguard.

27:31.320 --> 27:33.600
Little one,
you're not an impostor, are you?

27:33.680 --> 27:34.960
Watch your mouth.

27:35.040 --> 27:36.200
-What are you implying?
-The army's about to march.

27:36.280 --> 27:37.440
What's all this noise?

27:38.160 --> 27:39.000
Master Wu,

27:39.520 --> 27:40.480
these people…

27:44.800 --> 27:45.720
This…

27:53.400 --> 27:54.880
-All troops,
-What are you doing here?

27:54.960 --> 27:55.840
Assemble!

27:56.480 --> 27:58.880
General Wu, my husband is badly wounded.

27:59.760 --> 28:03.160
Please, for the sake of brotherhood,
pretend you didn't see this.

28:03.760 --> 28:06.520
When I return from this battle
with military merit,

28:06.600 --> 28:08.640
even if someone tries to charge
Yan Zheng, it won't matter.

28:08.720 --> 28:09.600
The Mar…

28:11.320 --> 28:12.760
Would your husband agree to this?

28:13.960 --> 28:15.520
-I drugged him.
-You…

28:16.840 --> 28:17.920
How could you be so reckless?

28:18.000 --> 28:20.960
Do you have any idea
how important he is to today's battle?

28:21.040 --> 28:22.280
He's not even a squad leader.

28:22.360 --> 28:23.800
How important could he be?

28:23.880 --> 28:25.560
At most, he'd kill a few more enemies.

28:25.640 --> 28:28.160
In his current condition,
he's worse off than I am.

28:28.240 --> 28:29.400
Where is he? I'm going to find him.

28:29.480 --> 28:30.320
It's too late.

28:31.000 --> 28:33.120
The drug is strong.

28:33.200 --> 28:34.680
He'll be out for a while.

28:36.520 --> 28:38.840
Shi Yue's men
have torn a gap in the vanguard.

28:38.920 --> 28:39.920
By the Strategist's order,

28:40.000 --> 28:41.600
the Left Guard
is to reinforce immediately.

28:41.680 --> 28:42.560
Hyah!

28:47.240 --> 28:49.280
-Vanguard, left flank, attention!
-Here.

28:49.360 --> 28:51.400
-Full speed.
-Yes, sir.

28:55.200 --> 28:56.440
You, go to the right flank reserve.

28:57.040 --> 28:59.360
You few, protect her.

28:59.440 --> 29:00.440
Got it.

29:02.960 --> 29:04.000
Quick, inform the Marquis.

29:04.080 --> 29:05.960
Tell him his wife
has gone to the battlefield.

29:21.400 --> 29:22.960
Gongsun Yin!

29:23.760 --> 29:25.240
You dare come down
and face me in single combat?

29:25.320 --> 29:26.920
Let's settle this!

29:27.520 --> 29:30.400
I'm a scholar, naturally no match for you.

29:30.480 --> 29:34.040
The Marquis of Wu'an is waiting
to have tea with General Shi Yue.

29:44.440 --> 29:45.720
Got to say,

29:45.800 --> 29:48.400
Mrs. Fan's tactic of riling them up
works pretty well.

29:48.480 --> 29:50.120
This is outrageous!

29:50.640 --> 29:51.480
Gongsun Yin,

29:52.280 --> 29:53.240
you coward!

29:53.320 --> 29:55.840
Why don't you come down
and fight like a man?

29:59.960 --> 30:01.560
As you wish.

30:10.680 --> 30:12.520
Reserve Battalion, assemble!

30:12.600 --> 30:13.720
Reserve Battalion, assemble!

30:13.800 --> 30:15.640
Reserve Battalion, assemble!

30:16.960 --> 30:18.480
-Hurry!
-Even the reserves are going in?

30:18.560 --> 30:19.920
What kind of state must the front be in?

30:20.000 --> 30:21.320
Reserve Battalion, assemble!

30:21.840 --> 30:23.200
Quick!

30:25.800 --> 30:26.840
Assemble!

30:30.560 --> 30:31.880
How should we fight this battle?

30:33.360 --> 30:34.680
We should focus on staying alive.

30:35.800 --> 30:36.840
Man Di,

30:37.400 --> 30:39.200
when we get on the battlefield,
stick close to me.

30:39.280 --> 30:40.120
Don't get lost.

30:40.200 --> 30:41.960
If things get really bad, hide behind me.

30:42.040 --> 30:43.320
Okay, Sister.

30:44.880 --> 30:46.240
After this battle,

30:46.320 --> 30:47.880
we can go home
and have a good meal, right?

30:49.240 --> 30:50.080
Probably.

30:50.600 --> 30:51.680
Let's just stay alive first.

30:51.760 --> 30:52.600
No more talk!

30:52.680 --> 30:54.360
Await orders from the front.

31:09.360 --> 31:11.040
Look, fog.

31:35.800 --> 31:36.960
There's blood in the fog.

31:38.160 --> 31:40.360
All troops, on alert. Draw swords.

33:10.120 --> 33:12.040
Don't stay where you are. Charge out!

33:13.320 --> 33:14.320
Move!

33:16.960 --> 33:20.000
47, 48,

33:20.920 --> 33:24.000
49, 50.

33:29.760 --> 33:32.720
One, two…

33:36.160 --> 33:38.960
Brother-in-law, why are you awake?

33:40.120 --> 33:43.240
Sister told me to count to 1,000
and then poke you awake.

33:43.760 --> 33:47.080
But I don't know how to count to 1,000.

33:47.160 --> 33:49.360
She said when I get to 50,

33:49.440 --> 33:51.720
I put down a stone.

33:51.800 --> 33:54.440
I need to save up 20 stones.

33:54.520 --> 33:56.640
Why did you wake up early?

34:01.800 --> 34:02.920
Brother-in-law?

34:05.400 --> 34:06.320
Xie Jiu.

34:08.800 --> 34:09.639
Xie Jiu!

34:10.360 --> 34:11.199
Xie Jiu!

34:13.159 --> 34:15.120
-Marquis, there you are!
-What's going on?

34:15.199 --> 34:16.440
The battle situation is critical.

34:16.520 --> 34:17.960
Shi Yue has indeed abandoned Sui Yuanqing.

34:18.040 --> 34:20.520
Shi Hu is slaughtering a path through.
We can't hold much longer.

34:20.600 --> 34:22.480
Where did Sister go?

34:23.360 --> 34:24.440
Mrs. Fan…

34:25.400 --> 34:26.560
is on the front lines.

34:34.120 --> 34:34.960
Marquis, are you alright?

34:42.080 --> 34:43.600
Ning, turn around.

34:43.679 --> 34:44.920
Okay.

34:46.239 --> 34:48.320
Five, six,

34:49.560 --> 34:52.600
seven, eight,

34:52.679 --> 34:55.639
nine, ten.

34:55.719 --> 34:57.920
-Bring me my armor.
-Yes, sir.

35:47.640 --> 35:49.000
A good pig in this life.

35:49.840 --> 35:51.240
Be a good person in the next.

35:53.320 --> 35:55.640
A few of you, go smash those catapults.

35:59.040 --> 36:01.040
Don't just stand there. Charge!

36:02.040 --> 36:03.200
Charge.

36:03.280 --> 36:04.720
Charge!

36:19.440 --> 36:20.480
Marchioness.

37:44.720 --> 37:46.240
The Yanzhou army is useless.

37:46.320 --> 37:47.960
Not a single one worth fighting.

37:48.560 --> 37:49.400
General Wu.

37:50.360 --> 37:51.960
Tell the Marquis of Wu'an
to come out and die.

37:54.520 --> 37:55.960
If you don't hand it over,

37:56.040 --> 37:58.760
your heir won't be an heir anymore.

37:59.720 --> 38:02.040
You're that woman who humiliated
the heir the other day.

38:02.640 --> 38:03.840
Coming to battle with a little knife,

38:04.840 --> 38:05.840
who do you think you're mocking?

38:06.680 --> 38:09.000
Today, I'm going to smash you into a pulp.

38:16.680 --> 38:17.960
Fan, you okay?

38:41.600 --> 38:42.760
Die!

40:29.840 --> 40:31.400
Fan!

40:44.080 --> 40:46.640
Shi Hu is dead! We've won!

40:47.880 --> 40:50.040
Shi Hu is dead! We've won!

40:50.120 --> 40:51.760
Fan, you alright?

40:52.680 --> 40:54.920
We've won!

40:56.800 --> 40:58.240
Look, it's the Marquis of Wu'an!

41:01.120 --> 41:02.800
The Marquis is here!

41:02.880 --> 41:04.040
Marquis of Wu'an.

41:04.640 --> 41:05.520
Marquis of Wu'an!

41:05.600 --> 41:09.120
Marquis of Wu'an!

41:09.200 --> 41:12.240
Marquis of Wu'an!

41:12.320 --> 41:13.320
Does he look like…

41:15.640 --> 41:16.840
A little.

41:18.280 --> 41:19.600
It's…

41:19.680 --> 41:20.680
The more I look,
the more he looks like him.

42:43.040 --> 42:44.040
Oh no.

45:29.880 --> 45:33.040
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS FILM

45:33.120 --> 45:34.000
Subtitle translation by: Wanjiao Song
